ARP

How to open an Admin Command Prompt
  Search Powershell in windows search
  Right click and select run as administrator 
  
 Ipconfig
   list IP information such as Ipv4/6, default gatewall, subnet
   ipconfig /all gives detailed information on all network adapter
   
Wireshark
  Used to log network communication between Pc and network
  can obtain MAC's fro pining IP
  detailed description of communication 
  can see broadcasts and what is being broadcast
